Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
signoffTimeDesign(25.10)                              signoffTimeDesign(25.10)

Name
       signoffTimeDesign  -  Runs  signoff  timing  analysis  using extraction
       (Quantus) and Tempus in batch mode, and generates  timing  reports  and
       ECO DB for each view

Syntax
       signoffTimeDesign

       [-help]

       [-noEcoDB]

       [-noExpandedViews]

       [-outDir <string>]

       [-prefix <string>]

       [-reportFullClockPath]

        [-reportOnly]

       Runs  signoff  timing analysis using extraction (Quantus) and Tempus in
       batch mode, and generates timing reports and ECO DB for each view.  The
       command  prints  out  a timing summary table per view and all the views
       combined.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       -noEcoDB
              Disables generation of ECO timing DB.

       -noExpandedViews
              Disables printing of expanded timing per view.

       -outDir <string>
              Specifies the directory to save reports.

       -prefix <string>
              Specifies prefix for timing report file names.

       -reportFullClockPath
              When this parameter is specified,  the  detailed  timing  report
              that is generated contains the full clock path.

       -reportOnly
              Skips parasitic extraction and use the parasitics in memory.

